{"tid":384264,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實肥姐檔野有咩咁好食？","createTime":"2017-09-02T07:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T22:31:47.000Z","uid":6034,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cec11ceddb27435103ea38210a130635ed7a23b0","tid":384264,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/151944_0cbde60124089681fd153fc823840ec5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F151944_0cbde60124089681fd153fc823840ec5.jpg&h=834f4339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我加左甜醬只食到甜醬味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊嘢本身完全無味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bdd76a376c5893bfa8c1163b5b9bc8f2a7b464","tid":384264,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"證明你平開食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  食到無撚左味覺"},{"pid":"ec561352375cd0b4a8b1fe81ec3e39969a3355d2","tid":384264,"uid":28913,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明你平開食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  食到無撚左味覺</blockquote><br />\n肥姐檔野之前比新聞爆污糟過廁所板喎, 唔知謗個先食開屎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f27e35cfb3f7f8cd15c20f675153ed8ba5246a","tid":384264,"uid":6034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"有無食家係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710c495d14bdaab274dcaa6d4685035993f81b3e","tid":384264,"uid":126046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"認同 想當年可能真係好食<br />\n但今時今日已經搵唔到食佢巴理由"},{"pid":"1b90d997d12f9dad2b122e35aefbfb9576eb2744","tid":384264,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:26:51.000Z","msg":"串鳩gordon ramsay既肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387c5742a52c9b5298d7450ec4ebd5481bf5577c","tid":384264,"uid":121868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T21:58:47.000Z","msg":"即係如果係好撚好食既野就一定要讚,<br />\n但呢D野食過一次就算架啦, 又唔係好撚好食又唔係平,<br />\n次次去好景經過都見到排哂長龍,<br />\n係咪真係咁多人未食過"},{"pid":"7dbc6f7fe34b85341f16a8f2fe0113e7484b05cf","tid":384264,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T22:31:47.000Z","msg":"演員黎"}]}